title: The Violent Delights of NFC Westworld
description:
Mina and Domonique Foxworth discuss Patrick Mahomes' extension with the Chiefs before previewing the teams in the NFC West: Cardinals (7:00), Seahawks (19:42), 49ers (39:30), and Rams (52:10).
